{"tid":176101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"還只認識 Gigi、Bella Hadid？4 位「辣度破表」的歐美嫩模大集合","createTime":"2017-03-28T03:16:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T17:28:35.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fbca450be3f7cc6b7d17bb574f2338af8cc342e","tid":176101,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:16:13.000Z","msg":"提到歐美嫩模，你腦子裡第一個浮現的是誰呢？是來自卡達夏名媛家族的坎達兒珍娜（Kendall Jenner）？還是紅遍半遍天富二代姊妹花吉吉哈蒂德（Gigi Hadid）、貝拉哈蒂德（Bella Hadid）？或是作風大膽火辣的英國嫩模 - 艾蜜莉瑞特考斯基（Emily Ratajkowski）？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒關係，以上嫩模根本就是大明星等級了！喜新厭舊的山抓現在為您精心挑選更多辣到翻天的性感嫩模，你將會發現時尚圈實在是「長江後浪推前浪，年年總有辣模出」呀！<br />\n<br />\n夏洛特&middot;麥金妮 Charlotte McKinney<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64095/58d8c9633077d.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64095%2F58d8c9633077d.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a58af3ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23 歲 171cm  32F-26-36<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夏洛特&middot;麥金妮 2015 年憑著超級盃的漢堡廣告一夕爆紅，金髮碧眼的她形容自己是「以大胸部為特徵」，被外界封為「下一個凱特&middot;阿普頓」。而這位超級盃寶貝也曾經因為駭客入侵造成裸照外流，討論度瞬間爆表，成為 18 禁的話題人物。<br />\nIG 傳送門：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞秋庫克 Rachel Cook<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64095/58d8c95ebc3a7.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64095%2F58d8c95ebc3a7.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=57ca0276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21 歲 175cm 32B-24.5-35<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國華盛頓出生的瑞秋庫克擁有一張精緻臉蛋，光是深邃五官和湛藍雙眸就已經迷死不少人，而她妖嬈性感的曲線更是性感逼人。她纖瘦、高挑又有馬甲線和健美腹肌，加上她不吝惜在 IG 上分享自己的各種裸照，年僅 21 歲就擁有超過一百萬名粉絲，甚至比許多明星還要火紅呢。<br />\nIG 傳送門：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉&middot;帕爾文 Barbara Palvin<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64095/58d8c95d7d062.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64095%2F58d8c95d7d062.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=73e790de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23 歲 171cm 33B-23-35<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下一位登場的是匈牙利嫩模芭芭拉&middot;帕爾文，美的充滿仙氣的她曾經在電影《海克力士》客串一角，難怪大家是不是覺得她很眼熟呢？外表和身材都無懈可擊的芭芭拉&middot;帕爾文曾經為《維多利亞的秘密》走秀，就連小賈斯汀都曾經和她傳出緋聞，拜倒在她的石榴裙下呢。<br />\nIG 傳送門：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n卡梅拉蘿絲 Carmella Rose<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64095/58d8c95ae4b06.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64095%2F58d8c95ae4b06.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=73bca821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n21 歲 173 cm 32C-23-34<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n來自美國加州的嫩模卡梅拉蘿絲是 95 後的新秀，受訪時她滿心期待著《體育畫報》的面試，希望能躍上性感畫報女郎之列。看看她逆天長腿和姣好面容，邁向超模之路對這位她來說絕非難事。作風直爽的卡梅拉蘿絲毫不諱言自己非常欣賞足球 C 羅，希望有幸能和 C 羅約會，直接告白可以說是超級敢的啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.juksy.com/files/articles/64095/58d8c9588a01e.jpg?m=widen&amp;i=600&amp;e=jpg&amp;q=75\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.juksy.com%2Ffiles%2Farticles%2F64095%2F58d8c9588a01e.jpg%3Fm%3Dwiden%26i%3D600%26e%3Djpg%26q%3D75&h=a33faf19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIG 傳送門：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朱千雪 Tracy Chu<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20161118/s00009/1479478742709_8BB1BBACF68FB97CF06E1CF1CAA2BBE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20161118%2Fs00009%2F1479478742709_8BB1BBACF68FB97CF06E1CF1CAA2BBE1.jpg&h=ec5b647f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n28 歲 166 cm 33S-24-35<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.tvb.com/event/misshk2012/album/1/1345816855_173_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.tvb.com%2Fevent%2Fmisshk2012%2Falbum%2F1%2F1345816855_173_o.jpg&h=0d522be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n壓軸登場的是香城共和國嫩模朱千雪，美的充滿仙氣的她曾經在電影《赤道》客串一角，難怪大家是不是覺得她很眼熟呢？外表和身材都無懈可擊的朱千雪曾經為《MAX&amp;Co》走時裝騷，就連小賈斯汀都曾經和她傳出緋聞，拜倒在她的石榴裙下呢。<br />\nIG 傳送門：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/tracytschu/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftracytschu%2F&d=GkFIyr4nU57GJWscoxyRLQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=d9f8f51d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/tracytschu/</a><br />\n<br />\n看完了這些憑年齡 22 歲的嫩模們，你是不是覺得她們當中有些有點眼熟，有些則是令人眼睛一亮呢？別害羞，快按下追蹤鍵！亮眼的她們，前途無可限量。搞不好這些花朵般模特兒們，明天就變成好萊塢的大明星也說不定呢！"},{"pid":"0b59d73b886d04030b2c79a7ad3667dfc216d889","tid":176101,"uid":50286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bedec8b340b72a5592eda4793b6d802e094e990a","tid":176101,"uid":93880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"Rachel cook 粉絲一號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b841b2aeffb1f41e1727b7b0f067a6d024515cad","tid":176101,"uid":6786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"33S<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e035d07ce2d468d748682da97b3d2e7c416111e","tid":176101,"uid":78411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:22:43.000Z","msg":"朱千雪!!!"},{"pid":"deee35c88e378b8c17df93508ea39c333dd954f1","tid":176101,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:30:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朱千雪!!!</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3og0IMh1KyqjTfCosU/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"htt